\v 4 Njalo uzakwehliselwa phansi\x + Luka 19.44.\x*, ukhulume usemhlabathini, lenkulumo yakho izakuba phansi ethulini\x + 26.16.\x*, lelizwi lakho lizakuba njengeloledlozi\x + 8.19.\x* liphuma emhlabathini, lenkulumo yakho ibe ngumlozwi ophuma othulini\x + 8.19.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo ixuku labezizwe bakho lizakuba njengothuli olucholekileyo\x + 25.5. 29.20.\x*, lexuku labalesihluku\x + 25.5. 29.20.\x* njengamakhoba adlulayo\x + Hlab. 1.4.\x*. Yebo, kuzahle kube masinyane\x + 30.13. Nani 6.9.\x*.
\v 6 Uzakwethekelelwa yiN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla\x + 24.22. Hez. 38.8.\x* ngomdumo, langokuzamazama komhlaba, lomsindo omkhulu, isivunguzane, lesiphepho\x + 28.2.\x*, lelangabi lomlilo oqothulayo\x + 30.30.\x*.
