\v 8 Kuzakuba lanjengolambileyo ephupha\x + Jobe 20.8.\x*\x + Hlab. 73.20.\x*, khangela-ke, uyadla, kodwa aphaphame\x + Hlab. 73.20.\x*, lomphefumulo wakhe ungelalutho; loba njengowomileyo ephupha, khangela-ke, uyanatha, kodwa aphaphame, khangela-ke uphelelwa ngamandla, lomphefumulo wakhe uyalangatha\x + Hlab. 107.9.\x*; lizakuba njalo ixuku lazo zonke izizwe ezilwa zimelene lentaba iZiyoni.
