\v 9 Manini, lithithibale; zithokoziseni liphumputheke; badakiwe\x + 19.14.\x*, kodwa hatshi ngewayini\x + 51.21.\x*; bayadiyazela, kodwa hatshi ngenxa yokunathwayo okulamandla.
\v 10 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\x + Roma 11.8.\x*\nd* ithululele phezu kwenu umoya wobuthongo obunzima\x + Jobe 4.13.\x*, yavala amehlo enu\x + 6.10.\x*; abaprofethi lezinhloko zenu, ababoni, ibagubuzele.
