\v 11 Lawo wonke umbono\x + 2 Kor. 3.14,15.\x* usube kini njengamazwi ogwalo olunanyekiweyo\x + 8.16. Dan. 12. 4.\x* okuthi balunika owazi umbhalo, besithi: Bala lokhu siyakuncenga; yena athi: Ngingeke, ngoba lunanyekiwe\x + 8.16. Dan. 12. 4.\x*.
\v 12 Ugwalo beselunikwa ongazi umbhalo, besithi: Bala lokhu, siyakuncenga; yena athi: Kangiwazi umbhalo.
